ause he cares, is a perfectionist and uses the very best equipment and software to deliver pictures beyond compare.[/wr_vc_testimonial][wr_vc_testimonial clientname=\\\"Rebecca Muise\\\" image=\\\"2847\\\"]COMMUNITY \\u0026 MARKETING MANAGER\\n\\nAs a custom home design firm we rely on professional, high quality photography to capture the beauty in our designs. Jason Hartog Photography never disappoints. His attention to detail is unmatched. His technique is top notch. His photography highlights the most compelling details in the design and creates a visual that we are proud to showcase in our portfolio. We highly recommend Jason Hartog Photography for professional interior and exterior architectural photography.[/wr_vc_testimonial][wr_vc_testimonial clientname=\\\"Denise O'connel\\\" image=\\\"2849\\\"]FREELANCE PRODUCER, DIRECTOR AND JOURNALIST\\n\\nJason has a keen eye for good visuals. He goes beyond taking beautiful photographs, and tells the story behind them. He is talented, hard-working, motivated and driven, meaning that he gets the job done on time and on budget. I would recommend Jason to any potential client, without hesitation.[/wr_vc_testimonial][/wr_vc_testimonials]\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"5:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"main\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex flex-col md:flex-row h-[80dvh] overflow-hidden pl-8 md:pl-16\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"md:w-1/2 flex-none\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"img\\\",null,{\\\"src\\\":\\\"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/9jt26sz2/jasonhartog/6aaeebb0e24f323ca06b9d3d7aed183f57233d35-8044x5916.jpg?w=800\\u0026q=80\\\",\\\"alt\\\":\\\"Testing\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"w-full h-full object-cover\\\"}]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"md:w-1/2 px-8 md:px-16 py-16 overflow-y-auto\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h1\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-black mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Jason Hartog\