 Over the past years, Jason has specialized in architectural interior and exterior photography, providing images for leading consumer publications, high-end architects and designers, and retailers in that space. Prior to that, he has gained experience capturing stunning images for the automotive, electronics, and apparel industries. Jason is also teaching the next generation of photographers how to use the lens, digital tools and new technology to capture beauty, relay stories, and decipher life. He teaches at Fanshawe College in the 3rd year of the Advanced Photography Program, where he also helped to develop the program curriculum. He lives in Guelph, Ontario, Canada with his wife and three children. 14:T69a,wr_vc_testimonials][wr_vc_testimonial clientname=\"Georgette McCulloch\" image=\"2843\"]EDITOR IN CHIEF - OUR HOMES MAGAZINE GROUP\nPhotographing interior spaces is an art. Professional photographer Jason Hartog is our artist.  Jason’s technical and visual skills make him the best in the business.\nJason has been photographing interiors for OUR HOMES Media Group for more than a decade and he just keeps getting better. Our publications shine because of Jason.\nHe’s not only a total pro, but our clients love working with him because he cares, is a perfectionist and uses the very best equipment and software to deliver pictures beyond compare.[/wr_vc_testimonial][wr_vc_testimonial clientname=\"Rebecca Muise\" image=\"2847\"]COMMUNITY & MARKETING MANAGER\n\nAs a custom home design firm we rely on professional, high quality photography to capture the beauty in our designs. Jason Hartog Photography never disappoints. His attention to detail is unmatched. His technique is top notch. His photography highlights the most compelling details in the design and creates a visual that we are proud to showcase in our portfolio. We highly recommend Jason Hartog Photography for professional interior and exterior architectural photography.[/wr_vc_testimonial][wr_vc_testimonial clientname=\"Denise O'connel\" image=\"2849\"]FREELANCE PRODUCER, DIRECTOR AND JOURNALIST\n\nJason has a keen eye for good visuals. He goes beyond taking beautiful photographs, and tells the story behind them. He is talented, hard-working, motivated and driven, meaning that he gets the job done on time and on budget. I would recommend Jason to any potential client, without hesitation.[/wr_vc_testimonial][/wr_vc_testimonials]5:[\"$\",\"main\",null,{\"className\":\"flex flex-col md:flex-row h-[80dvh] overflow-hidden pl-8 md:pl-16\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"md:w-1/2 flex-none\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"img\",null,{\"src\":\"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/9jt26sz2/jasonhartog/6aaeebb0e24f323ca06b9d3d7aed183f57233d35-8044x5916.jpg?w=800&q=80\",\"alt\":\"Testing\",\"className\":\"w-full h-full object-cover\"}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"md:w-1/2 px-8 md:px-16 py-16 overflow-y-auto\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-black mb-4\",\"children\":\"Jason Hartog\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm italic text-gray-600 mb-8\",\"children\":\"To me, photography is really is the perfect blend of technology, chemistry and creativity, that in the hands of a true craftsmen has produced some of the most stunning works of art known to man.--Jason Hartog\"}],[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"bio\":[{\"_key\":\"e95e5758e044\",\"_type\":\"block\",\"children\":[{\"_key\":\"8073198e2fff\",\"_type\":\"span\",\"marks\":[],\"text\":\"$13\"}],\"markDefs\":[],\"style\":\"normal\"}],\"clients\":null,\"testimonials\":[{\"clientName\":\"Bob\",\"clientTitle\":null,\"quote\":\"$14\"}]}]]}]]}]\n","/about/__PAGE__":"1:\"$Sreact.fragment\"\n2:I[52059,[\"/_next/static/chunks/0.gl895ocyq5_.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0sh.6aqimy6c9.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0o_dm_on1l196.js\"],\"default\"]\n7:I[97367,[\"/_next/static/chunks/0.gl895ocyq5_.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0sh.6aqimy6c9.js\"],\"OutletBoundary\"]\n8:\"$Sreact.suspense\"\n:HL[\"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/9jt26sz2/jasonhartog/6aaeebb0e24f323ca06b9d3d7aed183f57233d35-8044x5916.jpg?w=800&q=80\",\"image\"]\n3:T4a5,Becoming a photographer is an obvious choice for Jason; it gives him the opportunity to be creative, meet great people, and play with cool gadgets. He printed his first 8x10 in the high school dark room, and since then the magic of capturing the perfect exposure has him hooked. Since those days rocking the paper gently back and forth in the tray, Jason has spent almost every day of the past 15 years taking beautiful photographs that tell impactful stories for his clients. Over the past years, Jason has specialized in architectural interior and exterior photography, providing images for leading consumer publications, high-end architects and designers, and retailers in that space. Prior to that, he has gained experience capturing stunning images for the automotive, electronics, and apparel industries. Jason is also teaching the next generation of photographers how to use the lens, digital tools and new technology to capture beauty, relay stories, and decipher life. He teaches at Fanshawe College in the 3rd year of the Advanced Photography Program, where he also helped to develop the program curriculum. He lives in Guelph, Ontario, Canada with his wife and three children. 4:T69a,wr_vc_testimonials][wr_vc_testimonial clientname=\"Georgette McCulloch\" image=\"2843\"]EDITOR IN CHIEF - OUR HOMES MAGAZINE GROUP\nPhotographing interior spaces is an art. Professional photographer Jason Hartog is our artist.  Jason’s technical and visual skills make him the best in the business.\nJason has been photographing interiors for OUR HOMES Media Group for more than a decade and he just keeps getting better. Our publications shine because of Jason.\nHe’s not only a total pro, but our clients love working with him because he cares, is a perfectionist and uses the very best equipment and software to deliver pictures beyond compare.[/wr_vc_testimonial][wr_vc_testimonial clientname=\"Rebecca Muise\" image=\"2847\"]COMMUNITY & MARKETING MANAGER\n\nAs a custom home design firm we rely on professional, high quality photography to capture the beauty in our designs. Jason Hartog Photography never disappoints. His attention to detail is unmatched. His technique is top notch. His photography highlights the most compelling details in the design and creates a visual that we are proud to showcase in our portfolio. We highly recommend Jason Hartog Photography for professional interior and exterior architectural photography.[/wr_vc_testimonial][wr_vc_testimonial clientname=\"Denise O'connel\" image=\"2849\"]FREELANCE PRODUCER, DIRECTOR AND JOURNALIST\n\nJason has a keen eye for good visuals. He goes beyond taking beautiful photographs, and tells the story behind them. He is talented, hard-working, motivated and driven, meaning that he gets the job done on time and on budget. I would recommend Jason to any potential client, without hesitation.[/wr_vc_testimonial][/wr_vc_testimonials]0:{\"rsc\":[\"$\",\"$1\",\"c\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"main\",null,{\"className\":\"flex flex-col md:flex-row h-[80dvh] overflow-hidden pl-8 md:pl-16\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"md:w-1/2 flex-none\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"img\",null,{\"src\":\"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/9jt26sz2/jasonhartog/6aaeebb0e24f323ca06b9d3d7aed183f57233d35-8044x5916.jpg?w=800&q=80\",\"alt\":\"Testing\",\"className\":\"w-full h-full object-cover\"}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"md:w-1/2 px-8 md:px-16 py-16 overflow-y-auto\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-black mb-4\",\"children\":\"Jason Hartog\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm italic text-gray-600 mb-8\",\"children\":\"To me, photography is really is the perfect blend of technology, chemistry and creativity, that in the hands of a true craftsmen has produced some of the most stunning